".. versionchanged:: version number\n"
"\n"
"    This and that changed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../contributors_manual/krita_manual_readme.rst:393
msgid ""
"In all cases, check if you want to add yourself to the author field in the "
"metadata section on top."
